
Available targets:

make doc                    create all documentation (except man pages and epub)
make man                    create man pages
make doc-doxygen            build HTML and man version of doxygen documentation
make doc-html               build HTML version of the manual (one big html only)
make doc-html-chunked       build chunked HTML version of the manual
make doc-pdf                build PDF version of the manual
make epub                   build EPUB version of the manual

make check                  test the validity of the documenation source and tools

